languages.text: "Скромные завсегдатаи "Амасекуса" поведают правнукам, что им выпала честь лицезреть ваш визит в это недостойное вашей ослепительности место, шерин. Если, конечно, доживут до того, чтобы увидеть правнуков".

"The lowly regulars of the Amasecus will be telling their great-grandchildren about the time they had the honour of witnessing your dazzling visit to that unworthy dive, shereen. That is, of course, if they live long enough to see their great-grandchildren."

languages.text: “到时候，烈酒修会那些卑微的老主顾，肯定会和他们的曾孙子讲述他们是怎么亲眼看到你大驾光临，亲爱的。不过当然，前提是他们得能活到有曾孙子的时候。”

languages.text: 「アマセックをよく飲んでる卑しい連中は、あの不相応なダイブへのアンタのまばゆいばかりの訪問を目撃する栄誉を得た時のことを、ひ孫にまで語り継ぐだろうさ。もちろん、ひ孫の代まで長生きすればの話だけどね」

languages.text: «Los rastreros parroquianos del Amasecus les hablarán a sus bisnietos del día en el que tuvieron el honor de presenciar su gloriosa visita a ese cuchitril de mala muerte, shereen. Bueno, suponiendo que vivan para conocer a sus bisnietos».
languages.original_text: "The lowly regulars of the Amasecus will be telling their great-grandchildren about the time they had the honour of witnessing your dazzling visit to that unworthy dive, shereen. That is, of course, if they live long enough to see their great-grandchildren."

languages.text: « Les modestes habitués de l'Amasecus raconteront à leurs arrière-petits-enfants qu'ils ont eu l'honneur d'être témoins de votre majestueuse visite dans ce tripot de bas étage, shereen. Enfin, à condition qu'ils vivent assez longtemps pour avoir des arrière-petits-enfants. »
languages.original_text: "The lowly regulars of the Amasecus will be telling their great-grandchildren about the time they had the honour of witnessing your dazzling visit to that unworthy dive, shereen. That is, of course, if they live long enough to see their great-grandchildren."

languages.text: "Die gemeinen Stammgäste des Amasecus werden noch ihren Urenkeln davon erzählen, wie ihnen die Ehre zuteilwurde, Zeuge Eures schillernden Besuchs in dieser unwürdigen Spelunke zu werden, Shereen. Natürlich nur, falls sie lange genug leben, um ihre Urenkel kennenzulernen."

languages.text: "Amasekus'un avam müdavimleri, senin o sana layık olmayan batağı ziyaret ederek ortamı aydınlatışına şahit olma onuruna eriştiklerini küçük küçük torunlarına anlatacaklar şirinim. Elbette küçük küçük torunlarını görecek kadar uzun yaşarlarsa."
